              <text><citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM233635">Section 68(11)</extref></citation> is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1">If paragraph (b) of the definition of contaminated land applies, a</amend.in> and substituting <amend.in quote="1">A</amend.in>.</text>
